posting_body: ['We are open for business!', 'We are now offering in person tours Monday-Saturday.', 'Contact us today to schedule a tour!', 'Texas Living.', 'Impeccably Crafted.', 'The luxury doesn’t stop when you leave your front door.', 'Our Pflugerville homes offer many community amenities for you to pamper yourself with.', 'Relax and visit the clubhouse, or take a cool and refreshing dip in the sparkling swimming pool while catching some daytime rays on the pool deck.', 'We are a pet-friendly community so bring your furry friends along.', 'For your active lifestyle, we also have a state-of-the-art fitness center.', 'Call us today and make an appointment and see why Legacy Rental Homes is the perfect place for you to call home.', 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'x 122', 'OR Text', '122', 'to', 'show contact info', 'to chat!', 'Follow This Link for More Information:', '<URL>', 'This is a 3 Bedroom, 2 Bath, approximately 1440 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Features', '- Wood Flooring', '- White Speckled or Slate Grey Quartz Countertops', '- Irrigation Water Sensors', '- Gas Range', '- Farm White or Trendy Grey Cabinetry', '- 2 Inch Faux Wood Blinds', '- White Subway Tile Backsplash', '- Stainless Steel Whirlpool Energy Efficient Appliances', '- Smart Thermostats', '- Stand Up Showers', '- Washer and Dryer Connections', '- Front Yard and Fenced Private Back Yards', '- Stand Alone Homes', '- 2 Car Attached Garage', '- LED Lighting', '*In Select Rental Homes', 'Community Amenities', '- Fitness Center', '- Amenity Center and Clubhouse with Wi-Fi', '- Hassle Free Lawncare', '- On-site Professional Management', '- Resort-style Swimming Pool', '- On-site Professional Maintenance', '- Park and Picnic Areas with Barbecue Grills', 'Pet Policy', 'Pets Welcome Upon Approval.', 'Office Hours', 'Monday-Tuesday: 9:00AM-6:00PM', 'Thursday-Friday: 9:00AM-6:00PM', 'Legacy', '1108 Legacy Drive, Pflugerville, TX, 78660', '8oSUueg4wfg']
